y) to cover the spread and for your bet to win. If the LA Kings&nbsp;win, they must do so by 1.5 runs or more (two or more in reality) for your bet to win. If the spread is set at a whole number E.g. LA Kings&nbsp;-1 @ Boston Bruins+1 and your team wins/loses by that exact number of runs&nbsp;then your bet is considered a push and your stake will be refunded.</li><li><b>Alternative Puck Line&nbsp;&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;the same as above but we alter the standard run line to a different number of runs. These are essential for backing our daily banker doubles where we use the line a lot.</li><li><strong>Game Totals&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>the total number of goals&nbsp;scored in the game by both sides. This bet works just like Football<strong>.&nbsp;</strong>E.g. LA Kings @ Boston Bruins&nbsp; Over/Under 5.5 goals&nbsp;means we need 6 goals&nbsp;or more to win the Overs and 5 goals or less to win the Unders. As with the puck line, if the game total&nbsp;is a whole number E.g. 5&nbsp;and the total goals&nbsp;scored are 5, then your bet becomes a push and your stake is refunded.</li><li><strong>Alternative Game Totals &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;the same as the previous but just a different number of goals. Found under the main props tab then&nbsp;alternative totals.</li><li><b>Parlay &nbsp;</b>a parlay is a term the Americans use for accumulators.</li></ul><p>We hope you enjoy our free NHL&nbsp;betting tips. Our aim is to provide free predictions every week but please remember to have fun and gamble responsibly.&nbsp;Enjoy watching the games and good luck!</p></div>','NHL Tips','','publish','closed','closed','','nhl-tips','','','2018-01-16 06:49:23','2018-01-16 06:49:23','',0,'http://localhost/sirtips/?page_id=159',0,'page','',0),(160,1,'2017-12-06 05:51:34','2017-12-06 05:51:34','<div class=\"ui horizontal divider invis_clss\" style=\"margin-top:1em;\"><i class=\"ui white custom info icon\"></i> More Info</div>\r\nNo Current Tips','Rugby Tips','','publish','closed','closed','','rugby-t